{
    "chapter": [
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "I swear by the Day of Judgment"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "And I swear by the soul which is self blaming"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "Does man think that We will not gather his bones"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "Indeed, We were able to make his fingertips"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "No, man desires that he continue committing sins"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "He asks: \"When is the Day of Resurrection"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "So, when the sight is dazzled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "And the moon is eclipsed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "And the sun and moon are joined together"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "Man will say on that Day: \"Where can I escape"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "No. There is no refuge"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "To your Lord on that Day is the abode"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "Man will be told on that Day what he has put forward, and what he has done"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "No, man will testify against himself"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "Even though he puts forth his excuses"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "Do not move your tongue with it to make haste"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "It is for Us to gather it and relate it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "So when We relate it, you shall follow its revelation"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "Then it is for Us to clarify it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "Alas, you all like this world"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "And neglect the Hereafter"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Faces on that Day will be shining"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "Looking at their Lord"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "And faces on that Day will be gloomy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Thinking that a punishment is coming to them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "Alas, when it reaches the throat"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "And it will be said: \"Who can save him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "And he assumes it is the time of passing"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "And the leg is buckled around the other leg"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "To your Lord on that Day he will be driven"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 31,
            "text": "For he did not believe nor reach out"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 32,
            "text": "But he denied and turned away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 33,
            "text": "Then he went to his family admiring himself"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 34,
            "text": "Woe to you and woe to you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 35,
            "text": "Then woe to you and woe to you"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 36,
            "text": "Did man think that he will be left neglected"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 37,
            "text": "Was he not a seed from sperm put forth"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 38,
            "text": "Then he was a clot, so he was created and developed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 39,
            "text": "Then He made the two pairs, male and female"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 75,
            "verse": 40,
            "text": "Is One as such then not able to resurrect the dead"
        }
    ]
}